metadata.name: Premium Membership #1
metadata.description: Well hello, you magnificent human! Are you frequently hunting for hidden gems within the NFT space? Do you like collecting JPEGs that do more than just look nice? Or maybe you're just looking to instaflip, you shifty fucker. Regardless of why you chose to pick this card up, I hope that it brings you a bit of delight at this moment. Buckle up, Buttercup! You're in for a ride! Welcome to CREEK Plus.
